content: I cannot predict the future, but swiss skydiver has shown tremendous potential and is undoubtedly one of the most exciting horses to watch out for in the sport. she has a formidable record, having won several graded stakes and the coveted preakness stakes, and has shown that she is willing to challenge male horses and beat them. her determination and talent make her a strong contender in future races, as she continues to improve and mature. of course, horse racing is a competitive sport, and there will always be talented horses vying for the top spot, but swiss skydiver has certainly proved herself to be one of the best in her division.
